      "content": "i don't even know why i'm typing this. i just feel like i've completely hit a wall. after 5 years of this phd, the funding just... it's gone. the lab is basically empty now. i look at my desk and i don't even recognize myself anymore. everything i built is just gone and i'm just so incredibly tired of trying to fix things that are clearly broken. i just want the noise to stop.",
